<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>OnTrYbe Secure Login</title>

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:#f7f8fa;
    color:#1f2937;
}

.container{
    max-width:1400px;
    margin:auto;
    padding:40px 20px;
}

.login-layout{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
    gap:50px;
    align-items:center;
}

.brand h1{
    font-size:48px;
    color:#091f4d;
    margin-bottom:8px;
}

.brand p{
    color:#6b7280;
    margin-bottom:40px;
}

.hero-title{
    font-size:42px;
    line-height:1.2;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

.hero-text{
    color:#6b7280;
    line-height:1.8;
    margin-bottom:35px;
}

.security-list{
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    gap:22px;
}

.security-item{
    display:flex;
    gap:15px;
}

.security-icon{
    width:45px;
    height:45px;
    background:#eef4ff;
    border-radius:12px;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    color:#2753d7;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.security-item h4{
    margin-bottom:5px;
}

.security-item p{
    color:#6b7280;
    font-size:14px;
}

.status-box{
    margin-top:30px;
    background:#fff;
    border-radius:14px;
    padding:15px;
    border:1px solid #e5e7eb;
}

.status-green{
    color:#16a34a;
    font-weight:600;
}

.login-card{
    background:#fff;
    border-radius:24px;
    padding:35px;
    box-shadow:0 10px 35px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
}

.top-bar{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    margin-bottom:25px;
    font-size:14px;
}

.secure{
    color:#16a34a;
    font-weight:600;
}

.login-header{
    text-align:center;
    margin-bottom:30px;
}

.login-header h2{
    font-size:32px;
    margin-top:15px;
}

.login-header p{
    color:#6b7280;
}

.lock-icon{
    width:70px;
    height:70px;
    border-radius:50%;
    background:#f3f4f6;
    margin:auto;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    font-size:26px;
}

.form-group{
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

label{
    display:block;
    margin-bottom:8px;
    font-weight:600;
}

input{
    width:100%;
    padding:14px;
    border:1px solid #d1d5db;
    border-radius:10px;
    outline:none;
}

input:focus{
    border-color:#0a2d74;
}

.options{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    margin-bottom:20px;
    font-size:14px;
}

.options a{
    color:#2753d7;
    text-decoration:none;
}

.login-btn{
    width:100%;
    border:none;
    background:#091f4d;
    color:white;
    padding:15px;
    border-radius:10px;
    cursor:pointer;
    font-size:16px;
    font-weight:600;
}

.divider{
    text-align:center;
    margin:25px 0;
    color:#9ca3af;
}

.google-btn{
    width:100%;
    background:white;
    border:1px solid #d1d5db;
    padding:14px;
    border-radius:10px;
    font-weight:600;
    cursor:pointer;
}

.security-note{
    margin-top:20px;
    padding:18px;
    background:#f8fbff;
    border:1px solid #dbeafe;
    border-radius:14px;
}

.security-note h4{
    margin-bottom:8px;
}

.flow-section{
    margin-top:50px;
    background:#fff;
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:25px;
    border:1px solid #e5e7eb;
}

.flow-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
    gap:20px;
    margin-top:20px;
}

.flow-card{
    text-align:center;
}

.flow-card h4{
    margin:10px 0;
}

.flow-card p{
    color:#6b7280;
    font-size:14px;
}

.footer-cards{
    margin-top:30px;
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
    gap:15px;
}

.footer-box{
    background:#fff;
    padding:18px;
    border-radius:14px;
    border:1px solid #e5e7eb;
}

.repo{
    margin-top:30px;
    background:#fff;
    border-radius:14px;
    padding:20px;
    border:1px solid #e5e7eb;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
}

.repo a{
    color:#091f4d;
    text-decoration:none;
    font-weight:600;
}

.site-footer{
    margin-top:40px;
    text-align:center;
    color:#6b7280;
}

@media(max-width:900px){

.login-layout{
    grid-template-columns:1fr;
}

.flow-grid{
    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
}

.footer-cards{
    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
}

.hero-title{
    font-size:32px;
}

.brand h1{
    font-size:38px;
}

}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<div class="login-layout">

<div>

<div class="brand">
<h1>OnTrYbe</h1>
<p>Empowering Traders. Building Futures.</p>
</div>

<h2 class="hero-title">
Secure access to your trading world.
</h2>

<p class="hero-text">
OnTrYbe is a community-driven platform for framework updates,
open-source documentation and initiatives built for traders,
by traders.
</p>

<div class="security-list">

<div class="security-item">
<div class="security-icon">🛡</div>
<div>
<h4>Bank-Grade Security</h4>
<p>AES-256 encryption protection.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="security-item">
<div class="security-icon">🔒</div>
<div>
<h4>SSL/TLS Encrypted</h4>
<p>Secure connections using TLS 1.3.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="security-item">
<div class="security-icon">👆</div>
<div>
<h4>Multi-Factor Authentication</h4>
<p>Additional verification for your account.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="security-item">
<div class="security-icon">📱</div>
<div>
<h4>Device Verification</h4>
<p>Prevent unauthorized access attempts.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="security-item">
<div class="security-icon">✔</div>
<div>
<h4>Fraud Monitoring</h4>
<p>Real-time monitoring and risk protection.</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>

<div class="status-box">
<span class="status-green">Platform Security: Operational</span><br>
All systems active and monitored 24/7
</div>

</div>

<div>

<div class="login-card">

<div class="top-bar">
<span class="secure">🛡 Secure Login</span>
<span>🌐 English</span>
</div>

<div class="login-header">
<div class="lock-icon">🔒</div>
<h2>Welcome Back</h2>
<p>Log in to continue to OnTrYbe</p>
</div>

<form>

<div class="form-group">
<label>Email / Username</label>
<input type="text" placeholder="trader@example.com">
</div>

<div class="form-group">
<label>Password</label>
<input type="password" placeholder="••••••••••">
</div>

<div class="options">
<label><input type="checkbox"> Remember me</label>
<a href="#">Forgot Password?</a>
</div>

<button class="login-btn">
🔒 Secure Login
</button>

<div class="divider">
or continue with
</div>

<button type="button" class="google-btn">
Continue with Google
</button>

<div class="security-note">
<h4>Why security matters?</h4>
<p>
We use enterprise-grade security protocols
to protect your account, data and trades.
</p>
</div>

</form>

</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="flow-section">

<h3>Authentication Flow</h3>

<div class="flow-grid">

<div class="flow-card">
<h4>1. User</h4>
<p>Enter credentials</p>
</div>

<div class="flow-card">
<h4>2. Verify</h4>
<p>Identity & device verification</p>
</div>

<div class="flow-card">
<h4>3. Authenticate</h4>
<p>Encrypted authentication</p>
</div>

<div class="flow-card">
<h4>4. Access</h4>
<p>Secure dashboard access</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="footer-cards">

<div class="footer-box">
<h4>Privacy First</h4>
<p>We never share your personal data.</p>
</div>

<div class="footer-box">
<h4>Data Encrypted</h4>
<p>Protected at rest and in transit.</p>
</div>

<div class="footer-box">
<h4>Session Protection</h4>
<p>Automatic session monitoring.</p>
</div>

<div class="footer-box">
<h4>Anti-Phishing</h4>
<p>Protection against malicious attacks.</p>
</div>

</div>

<div class="repo">
<div>
<h4>Repository</h4>
<p>Open-source friendly and community driven.</p>
</div>

<a href="#">github.com/ontrybe/platform</a>
</div>

<div class="site-footer">
© 2026 OnTrYbe. All rights reserved.
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
